## Kubernetes Overlay Structure

```
infra/kubernetes/
├── base/                             # Shared: namespaces, RBAC, NetworkPolicies, Quotas
├── services/<name>/                  # Per-service: deployment, service, hpa, pdb
└── overlays/
    ├── docker-desktop/               # ← LOCAL MACHINE OVERLAY
    │   ├── kustomization.yaml        # Entry point: references base + all patches
    │   ├── configmap-env.yaml        # Default env (host.docker.internal)
    │   ├── configmap-env-local.yaml  # ← GITIGNORED — generated by tailscale-config.sh
    │   ├── configmap-env-ai.yaml     # AI namespace env (default)
    │   ├── configmap-env-ai-local.yaml # ← GITIGNORED — generated
    │   ├── patch-<service>.yaml      # Image swap (traefik/whoami) + reduced resources
    │   ├── patch-*-nodeport.yaml     # NodePort 30080/30081 for Tailscale
    │   └── patch-quota-*.yaml        # Reduced ResourceQuota for laptop
    ├── dev/                          # Dev cloud overlay
    ├── staging/                      # Staging cloud overlay
    └── production/                   # Production cloud overlay
```

**Apply local K8s:**
```bash
kubectl apply -k infra/kubernetes/overlays/docker-desktop
```

**Preview without applying:**
```bash
kubectl kustomize infra/kubernetes/overlays/docker-desktop | grep -E "^(kind|  image):"
```

