## Tailscale Networking Rules

| Machine Role | Command | DB URL in ConfigMap |
|-------------|---------|---------------------|
| Primary (hosts postgres/redis) | `tailscale-config.sh --primary` | `host.docker.internal:5432` |
| Secondary | `tailscale-config.sh --db-host <ts-ip>` | `<ts-ip>:5432` |

**Gitignored files** (machine-specific, never commit):
- `.env.tailscale`
- `infra/kubernetes/overlays/docker-desktop/configmap-env-local.yaml`
- `infra/kubernetes/overlays/docker-desktop/configmap-env-ai-local.yaml`

**Required open ports on Tailscale firewall / ACL:**

| Port | Service | Direction |
|------|---------|-----------|
| 5432 | PostgreSQL | Secondary → Primary |
| 6379 | Redis | Secondary → Primary |
| 30080 | api-gateway NodePort | Any machine → Any |
| 30081 | auth-service NodePort | Any machine → Any |

**Test connectivity:**
```bash
nc -zv 100.79.214.33 5432    # postgres
nc -zv 100.79.214.33 6379    # redis
nc -zv 100.79.214.33 30080   # api-gateway
```

