## Smoke Test Sequence

Run after any install or reinstall to verify the full stack:

```bash
# 1. Docker infra
docker exec medinovai-postgres pg_isready -U medinovai -d medinovai
docker exec medinovai-redis redis-cli -a localdev ping
curl -sf http://localhost:9090/-/healthy && echo "Prometheus OK"
curl -sf http://localhost:3000/api/health && echo "Grafana OK"

# 2. K8s pods running
kubectl get pods -n medinovai-services
kubectl get pods -n medinovai-ai

# 3. K8s NodePort services responding
curl -sf http://localhost:30080 | grep Hostname && echo "api-gateway OK"
curl -sf http://localhost:30081 | grep Hostname && echo "auth-service OK"

# 4. Tailscale cross-machine (run from a secondary machine)
nc -zv 100.79.214.33 5432
curl -sf http://100.79.214.33:30080 | grep Hostname
```

