## Stub Images in docker-desktop Overlay

All 6 app services use `traefik/whoami:latest` as placeholder. This image:
- Responds HTTP 200 to **any** path (including `/health`, `/ready`)
- Prints pod hostname, IP, and request headers
- Requires zero configuration
- Pulls from Docker Hub automatically

**Replace with real images when app code is built:**
```yaml
# In overlay kustomization.yaml
images:
  - name: traefik/whoami
    newName: ghcr.io/myonsite-healthcare/api-gateway
    newTag: v1.0.0
```

